---
description: Apply testing patterns. Use when writing or modifying tests.
globs: tests/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Test Structure:
- Unit tests: `tests/<module>/test_*.py`
- Test data: `tests/<module>/test_data/`

Patterns:
- AAA: Arrange, Act, Assert
- Use fixtures for shared setup
- Use parametrize for data-driven tests
